text: "No Debes Jugar" () is a song by American singer Selena. The song was the lead single from Selena Live! (1993). The song peaked at number three on the Hot Latin Tracks, Latin Regional Mexican Airplay and Latin Pop Airplay chart. == Chart == Chart (1993) Peak position U.S. Billboard Hot Latin TracksSelena - Music Sales Information.
